if they could possess it...

11
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:29,798
the great power of creation
would be theirs.

12
00:01:29,965 --> 00:01:32,342
And one day...

13
00:01:32,885 --> 00:01:35,470
the most daring of them all...

14
00:01:35,637 --> 00:01:40,017
