He was a demigod of the wind and sea.

16
00:01:47,649 --> 00:01:49,234
He was a warrior.

17
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,737
A trickster.

18
00:01:54,198 --> 00:01:57,284
A shapeshifter who
could change form...

19
00:01:57,451 --> 00:02:00,204
with the power of his magical fish hook.

20
00:02:02,039 --> 00:02:03,332
And his name...

21
