We are only here...

1079
01:17:07,753 --> 01:17:10,631
because you stole the heart
in the first place.

1080
01:17:11,924 --> 01:17:14,551
No, we're here because
the ocean told you you're special...

1081
01:17:14,718 --> 01:17:16,553
and you believed it.

1082
01:17:17,763 --> 01:17:20,265
I am Moana of Motunui.

1083
01:17:20,432 --> 01:17:22,643
-You will board my boat...
-Goodbye, Moana.

1084
01:17:23,018 --> 01:17:23,894
...sail across the sea...

1085
01:17:24,394 --> 01:17:25,229
I'm not killing myself...

1086
01:17:25,395 --> 01:17:26,647
so you can prove
you're something you're not!

1087
01:17:26,813 --> 01:17:28,106
...and restore the heart of Te Fiti!

1088
01:17:28,774 --> 01:17:31,151
The ocean chose me!

1089
01:17:32,110 --> 01:17:33,820
It chose wrong.

1090
01:17:43,539 --> 01:17:44,623
Maui!

1091
01:17:59,596 --> 01:18:02,099
Why did you bring me here?

1092
01:18:06,937 --> 01:18:08,981
I'm not the right person.

1093
01:18:11,775 --> 01:18:14,611
You have to choose someone else.

1094
01:18:16,947 --> 01:18:19,491
Choose someone else.

1095
01:18:20,284 --> 01:18:21,618
Please.

1096
01:18:40,721 --> 01:18:41,972
No.

1097
01:18:57,863 --> 01:19:00,157
You're a long ways past the reef.

1098
01:19:01,533 --> 01:19:02,534
Gramma?

1099
01:19:04,578 --> 01:19:07,539
Guess I chose the right tattoo.

1100
01:19:08,123 --> 01:19:09,583
Gramma!

1101
01:19:14,630 --> 01:19:16,715
I tried, Gramma.

1102
01:19:18,634 --> 01:19:20,344
I couldn't do it.

1103
01:19:21,094 --> 01:19:23,597
It's not your fault.

1104
01:19:23,764 --> 01:19:27,518
I never should have put so much
on your shoulders.

1105
01:19:28,352 --> 01:19:30,395
If you are ready to go home...

1106
01:19:31,855 --> 01:19:33,857
I will be with you.

1107
01:19:50,415 --> 01:19:52,084
Why do you hesitate?

1108
01:19:53,460 --> 01:19:55,128
I don't know.

1109
01:19:58,715 --> 01:20:01,093
I know a girl from an island

1110
01:20:02,094 --> 01:20:04,763
She stands apart from the crowd

1111
01:20:05,222 --> 01:20:08,225
She loves the sea and her people

1112
01:20:08,725 --> 01:20:10,894
She makes her whole family proud

1113
01:20:12,062 --> 01:20:14,731
Sometimes the world
seems against you

1114
01:20:15,482 --> 01:20:18,277
The journey may leave a scar

1115
01:20:18,443 --> 01:20:21,238
But scars can heal and reveal just

1116
01:20:21,405 --> 01:20:23,991
Where you are

1117
01:20:24,950 --> 01:20:27,911
The people you love will change you

1118
01:20:28,287 --> 01:20:31,164
The things you have
learned will guide you

1119
01:20:31,415 --> 01:20:34,751
And nothing on earth can silence

1120
01:20:34,918 --> 01:20:38,046
The quiet voice still inside you

1121
01:20:38,463 --> 01:20:41,592
And when that voice starts to whisper

1122
01:20:41,758 --> 01:20:44,428
Moana, you've come so far

1123
01:20:45,179 --> 01:20:46,930
Moana, listen

1124
01:20:47,097 --> 01:20:51,768
Do you know who you are?

1125
01:20:54,021 --> 01:20:55,439
Who am I?

1126
01:20:57,482 --> 01:21:00,944
I am a girl who loves my island

1127
01:21:01,320 --> 01:21:04,865
And the girl who loves the sea

1128
01:21:05,282 --> 01:21:08,327
It calls me

1129
01:21:10,454 --> 01:21:13,332
I am the daughter of the village chief

1130
01:21:13,874 --> 01:21:16,793
We are descended from voyagers

1131
01:21:17,211 --> 01:21:19,546
Who found their way across the world

1132
01:21:20,005 --> 01:21:21,882
They call me

1133
01:21:23,634 --> 01:21:26,303
I've delivered us to where we are

1134
01:21:26,803 --> 01:21:29,431
I have journeyed farther

1135
01:21:29,973 --> 01:21:32,351
I am everything I've learned and more

1136
01:21:32,726 --> 01:21:35,646
Still it calls me

1137
01:21:36,730 --> 01:21:38,982
And the call isn't out there at all

1138
01:21:39,149 --> 01:21:41,944
It's inside me

1139
01:21:42,402 --> 01:21:44,321
It's like the tide

1140
01:21:44,488 --> 01:21:48,825
Always falling and rising

1141
01:21:49,284 --> 01:21:51,662
I will carry you here in my heart

1142
01:21:51,828 --> 01:21:54,873
You remind me

1143
01:21:55,040 --> 01:21:58,001
That come what may

1144
01:21:58,168 --> 01:22:01,171
I know the way

1145
01:22:01,338 --> 01:22:05,926
I am Moana

1146
01:22:40,377 --> 01:22:42,671
I am Moana of Motunui.

1147
01:22:44,214 --> 01:22:45,632
Aboard my boat...

1148
01:22:45,716 --> 01:22:47,551
I will sail across the sea...

1149
01:22:47,926 --> 01:22:50,888
and restore the heart of Te Fiti.

1150
01:23:27,090 --> 01:23:29,176
Te Kā can't follow us into the water.

1151
01:23:29,927 --> 01:23:31,428
We make it past the barrier islands...

1152
01:23:32,262 --> 01:23:33,472
we make it to Te Fiti.

1153
01:23:34,014 --> 01:23:35,265
None of which you understand...

1154
01:23:36,016 --> 01:23:37,518
because you are a chicken.

1155
01:24:44,042 --> 01:24:45,043
No!

1156
01:24:46,336 --> 01:24:48,797
Heihei! No, no, no!

1157
01:24:50,340 --> 01:24:51,508
Nice work!

1158
01:25:00,976 --> 01:25:01,935
Te Fiti.

1159
01:25:27,544 --> 01:25:28,962
Maui!

1160
01:25:33,050 --> 01:25:34,009
You came back.

1161
01:25:37,930 --> 01:25:39,223
But your hook.

1162
01:25:39,389 --> 01:25:40,891
One more hit and...

1163
01:25:41,767 --> 01:25:43,227
Te Kā's gotta catch me first.

1164
01:25:46,396 --> 01:25:48,398
I got your back, Chosen One.

1165
01:25:48,899 --> 01:25:50,067
Go save the world.

1166
01:25:50,150 --> 01:25:50,943
Maui.

1167
01:25:51,860 --> 01:25:52,861
Thank you.

1168
01:25:53,862 --> 01:25:55,113
You're welcome.

1169
01:25:55,864 --> 01:25:57,449
Cheeeehoooo!

1170
01:26:16,218 --> 01:26:17,344
Hot-hot-hot, hot-hot-hot!

1171
01:26:28,814 --> 01:26:30,274
Hey, Te Kā!

1172
01:26:31,233 --> 01:26:32,025
Shark head!

1173
01:26:33,610 --> 01:26:34,653
Cheeeehoooo!

1174
01:26:45,122 --> 01:26:46,290
Moana!

1175
01:26:56,466 --> 01:26:58,385
Get the heart to the spiral!

1176
01:27:36,215 --> 01:27:38,300
Te Fiti...

1177
01:27:38,467 --> 01:27:39,885
it's gone.

1178
01:27:52,523 --> 01:27:54,191
Te Kā!

1179
01:28:30,143 --> 01:28:31,311
Let her come to me.

1180
01:28:54,751 --> 01:28:58,297
I have crossed the horizon to find you

1181
01:29:05,512 --> 01:29:07,848
I know your name

1182
01:29:11,685 --> 01:29:15,564
They have stolen the
heart from inside you

1183
01:29:20,277 --> 01:29:23,447
But this does not define you

1184
01:29:26,992 --> 01:29:30,954
This is not who you are

1185
01:29:32,623 --> 01:29:37,878
You know who you are

1186
01:29:44,718 --> 01:29:47,387
Who you truly are.

1187
01:30:10,619 --> 01:30:11,662
Te Fiti!

1188
01:30:52,160 --> 01:30:53,537
The chicken lives.

1189
01:30:55,372 --> 01:30:57,374
I'm sorry about your hook.

1190
01:30:57,875 --> 01:31:00,878
Well, hook, no hook...

1191
01:31:01,378 --> 01:31:02,963
I'm Maui.

1192
01:31:21,899 --> 01:31:23,650
Te Fiti!

1193
01:31:24,818 --> 01:31:26,737
Hey, I mean, how you been?

1194
01:31:29,990 --> 01:31:32,409
Look, what I did was...

1195
01:31:32,576 --> 01:31:33,994
wrong.

1196
01:31:34,161 --> 01:31:36,205
I have no excuse.

1197
01:31:36,830 --> 01:31:37,915
I'm sorry.

1198
01:31:46,924 --> 01:31:50,427
You know, it'd be rude to refuse
a gift from a goddess.

1199
01:31:51,553 --> 01:31:53,430
Cheeeehoooo!

1200
01:31:55,265 --> 01:31:56,308
Thank you.

1201
01:31:56,391 --> 01:31:59,019
Your kind gesture is
deeply appreciated.

1202
01:31:59,102 --> 01:32:00,103
Cheeeehoooo.

1203
01:32:48,819 --> 01:32:50,237
Gonna miss you, drumstick.

1204
01:32:50,404 --> 01:32:51,446
You could come with us, you know.

1205
01:32:52,364 --> 01:32:55,951
My people are going to need
a master wayfinder.

1206
01:32:57,494 --> 01:32:59,413
They already have one.

1207
01:33:17,806 --> 01:33:18,932
See you out there, Maui.

1208
01:33:19,850 --> 01:33:22,227
See you out there, Moana.

1209
01:33:22,811 --> 01:33:24,021
Cheeeehoooo!

1210
01:34:15,405 --> 01:34:17,032
Mom! Dad!

1211
01:34:17,199 --> 01:34:18,367
Moana!

1212
01:34:26,375 --> 01:34:30,921
I may have gone
a little ways past the reef.

1213
01:34:32,256 --> 01:34:33,882
It suits you.

1214
01:34:34,049 --> 01:34:34,842
She's back!

1215
01:34:35,259 --> 01:34:36,260
Moana!

1216
01:34:36,426 --> 01:34:37,427
Pua!

1217
01:34:39,805 --> 01:34:40,556
Moana!

1218
01:34:42,474 --> 01:34:44,017
Welcome home!

1219
01:35:33,942 --> 01:35:36,111
We set a course to find

1220
01:35:36,278 --> 01:35:40,532
A brand new island
everywhere we roam

1221
01:35:42,826 --> 01:35:45,204
We keep our island in our mind

1222
01:35:45,746 --> 01:35:50,042
And when it's time to find home
We know the way

1223
01:35:51,668 --> 01:35:54,630
We are explorers reading every sign

1224
01:35:55,297 --> 01:36:00,677
We tell the stories of our elders
In a never-ending chain

1225
01:36:07,142 --> 01:36:11,688
We know the way

1226
01:46:06,700 --> 01:46:08,076
Shiny

1227
01:46:08,619 --> 01:46:11,121
I'm so shiny

1228
01:46:11,747 --> 01:46:13,540
Didn't help me though, did it?

1229
01:46:13,707 --> 01:46:15,667
Still upside down here.

1230
01:46:15,834 --> 01:46:18,086
Just need a little push.

1231
01:46:20,255 --> 01:46:21,256
Can we be real?

1232
01:46:21,423 --> 01:46:24,801
If my name was Sebastian
and I had a cool Jamaican accent...

1233
01:46:24,968 --> 01:46:26,178
you'd totally help me.

1234
01:46:26,345 --> 01:46:27,971
You would. You know you would.
